le=Project Polaroid by Kool Keith on Apple Music|website=[[itunes]]|language=en-us|access-date=November 26, 2017}}</ref> and on June 28, 2006 in [[Japan]] via Swamp Records. Audio production of the project was entirely handled by TomC3, and featured guest appearances from [[Organized Konfusion]]'s [[Prince Po]], [[Masters of Illusion]]'s Motion Man, and [[Third Sight]]'s Roughneck Jihad. \n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing = \n| all_music = TomC3\n| title1 = Project Polaroid\n| length1 = 3:24\n| title2 = Space 8000\n| length2 = 3:38\n| title3 = Talk To The Romans\n| length3 = 3:06\n| title4 = Mechanical Mechanix\n| note4 = featuring [[Prince Po]]\n| length4 = 2:42\n| title5 = I\u2019m Libra\n| length5 = 3:22\n| title6 = Diamond District\n| length6 = 3:42\n| title7 = Rhyme That Quit\n| length7 = 3:05\n| title8 = Clubber Lang\n| note8 = featuring Motion Man\n| length8 = 2:17\n| title9 = Uphill...Strange\n| length9 = 4:49\n| title10 = Digital Engineering\n| length10 = 2:29\n| title11 = The Overviewer\n| length11 = 3:56\n| title12 = Feel Me\n| note12 = featuring Roughneck Jihad\n| length12 = 5:04\n| title13 = Midwestern Shoe Calhoun\n| length13 = 3:36\n| title14 = Photo Shop\n| length14 = 1:43\n| title15 = \n| note15 = \n| length15 = \n| total_length = 46:53\n}}{{tracklist | collapsed = yes | headline = [[Japan|Japanese]] edition bonus track \n|title15 = Digital Engineering | note15 = Remix | length15 = }}\n==Personnel==\n*[[Kool Keith|Keith Matthew Thornton]] \u2013 main artist, vocals\n*Tom Cleary \u2013 main artist, producer, recording, mixing\n*Raggedy Andy \u2013 recording, design, layout, photography\n*David Cheppa \u2013 mastering\n*Nadjib Boulaone \u2013 scratches\n*[[Prince Po|Lawrence Baskerville]] \u2013 featured artist (track 4)\n*Paul K. Laster \u2013 featured artist (track 8)\n*Roughneck Jihad \u2013 featured artist (track 12)\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"co